Posts: 598<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/15/02 3:20:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1561.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Debate on Your Character</span><hr size=1> Ok im game:<br>
<br>
I have no need to ebay my characters.  I would never do so.  I have invested 2 years into Itchibum and 1 year into Ichi.  They are mine and I have too many friends here and there that would be hurt if i did so.  Scratchy and I are both professionals and this selling buying stuff isnt necessary.<br>
<br>
Now....if my RL came to ruin and my wife and I were unable to provide for my 3 childeren etc etc etc....and I had an opportunity to sell these characters to pay the mortage, put food on the table and pay my heat and electric bills......I would sell them in a heart beat and not think twice.<br>
<br>
A few people have sold their characters at the end of the summer for tuition for school....I cant really hold that against them.  They are bettering their lives.<br>
<br>
I think what annoys many of us is that we grouped with Character X, helped outfit character X, formed relationships with Character X.....Character X ebays and goes to crappy Guild B or to some other unscrupulous person who is working directly against your guild.  That is why people get irritated.  Its not that the person selling cant be forgiven for having a good reason to do it......it just sucks who bought it.<br>
<br>
On this server....a non-blue (please VI help us keep it that way) server.... these type of things hit home as each of us has only 1 character (as a main, many have multiple accounts I know).  We form relationships/rivalries and to have them meddled with upsets us and pulls at the fabric of our community.  That ticks people off too.<br>
<br>
So yes I can understand why people might Ebay and no I dont really like it but realize that unless I want to be one of the hall monitors or school narks there isnt much I can do.  I just choose to play and keep having fun.<br>
<br>
Sir Ichi<br>
<br>
Gravelord of Resolution<br>
Black Knight of Oggok<br>
